{"tid":250344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國戰機東海上空攔截美國偵察機    同時派無人機到尖閣諸島","createTime":"2017-05-20T04:05:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-20T10:24:35.000Z","uid":58099,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"91d51669aac3b4313f5393228dbf24497ee10ca4","tid":250344,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T04:05:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/j5366656353x63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fj5366656353x63.jpg&h=d8d87acd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2017年5月20日 10:45<br />\n【Now新聞台】美國太平洋空軍公布，兩架中國戰機在東海上空攔截一架美軍核輻射偵察機，批評解放軍機師「不專業」，說美方正循適當的外交和軍事渠道跟中方溝通。美國傳媒報道，雙方軍機當時最近距離只有150呎。<br />\n<br />\n美國有線新聞網絡引述一名美國官員報道，兩架中國蘇-30戰機周三在東海國際空域攔截美國空軍的「不死鳳凰」WC-135偵察機，雙方最近距離只有150呎，其中一架蘇-30更曾在美軍偵察機上方倒轉飛。<br />\n<br />\n美軍WC-135偵察機主要用來探測大氣層空氣中的核子活動迹象，可用來搜集北韓核試的證據。美國空軍發言人說，偵察機當時正依照國際法執行例行任務。<br />\n<br />\n根據偵察機人員的初步報告，正循適當的外交和軍事渠道與中方溝通。<br />\n<br />\n今次中美軍機對峙是今年內至少第二次同類事件，二月份，美國海軍一架P-3C「獵戶座」海上巡邏機和解放軍空軍一架預警機在南海黃岩島附近空域相遇，雙方距離一度只有不足1000呎，被美軍太平洋司令部形容為中美軍機一次「不安全的互動」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/s4497156353x63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fs4497156353x63.jpg&h=8a6dc59a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，日本政府證實自衛隊戰機周5曾緊急升空，應對相信由中國派出的無人機。<br />\n<br />\n共同社報道，四艘中國海警船周四上午相繼駛入尖閣諸島，即中方稱釣魚島附近的領海，之後在海警船上空發現有疑似無人機物體飛行，自衛隊派出F-15戰機緊急升空應對。<br />\n<br />\n今次是日本方面首次在尖閣諸島一帶目擊無人機飛行。日本防衛相稻田朋美認為無人機侵犯了日本主權。"},{"pid":"5cf0523b021e5c5a2bc22febd14d45b124a64d5c","tid":250344,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T04:28:24.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"c5d6cf657fa3d539db8a50cb1589dde5cad69a6c","tid":250344,"uid":89190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T04:31:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/20/123147_524665c7790565ec0d76ba28d11ba68e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F20%2F123147_524665c7790565ec0d76ba28d11ba68e.jpg&h=dca9260e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/20/123148_a7851e93c6650659f277c7e5109e2223.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F20%2F123148_a7851e93c6650659f277c7e5109e2223.jpg&h=ba998490&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3a607f03df943cfed3ea47f42c5db41fa86fe04","tid":250344,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T05:31:19.000Z","msg":","},{"pid":"bbe095fcab6f93f33dc42954dc9ffd68769fb598","tid":250344,"uid":21716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T05:33:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/20/123147_524665c7790565ec0d76ba28d11ba68e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F20%2F123147_524665c7790565ec0d76ba28d11ba68e.jpg&h=dca9260e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/20/123148_a7851e93c6650659f277c7e5109e2223.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F20%2F123148_a7851e93c6650659f277c7e5109e2223.jpg&h=ba998490&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大陸機師做我諗炒左機"},{"pid":"4692d12ecca4c0e5a04a42f5f3a1d34724651047","tid":250344,"uid":987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T05:34:05.000Z","msg":"一野轟落去啦"},{"pid":"66c0f1dc5e06ed6dcc97ee1adc3464fb25de4b4d","tid":250344,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T05:35:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/20/123147_524665c7790565ec0d76ba28d11ba68e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F20%2F123147_524665c7790565e